http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: Parenting Education 1 addresses the knowledge, skills, attitudes and behaviors associated with becoming an educated parent. The knowledge obtained will give future parents the ability to provide care, guidance, and a nurturing environment for their children. Topics that will be covered in Parenting 1 include teen pregnancy, parenting roles and responsibilities, and careers that involve parenting.
